projects.title: Project One
projects.detail: Learning to build a variety of web projects helps prepare you to handle anything. It’s impossible to master every language or back-end framework. But exposing yourself to different project types and languages enables you to refine the most important skill a developer can have, problem-solving.Learning to build a variety of web projects helps prepare you to handle anything.
